    { name: 'STN2 Model Runner cross-station reach', filed: '041726', note: 'Model Runner Fleet-bound at 10.0.0.2:12434. Self-reach verified on STN2. Cross-station reach from DPSL/DPSR/TRP0/GOG1/CUBE expected, not yet empirically tested — run Invoke-RestMethod on each at next boot. Full context: RELAY/RESEARCH_ModelRunnerSTN2_FleetBinding_Trip_041726.md. Verified from ODT 041726 23:22.' },
