    { name: 'Tailscale mesh VPN on every station', filed: '041326 (promoted NEAR 041726 22:46 by Dan)', note: 'Dan: "We need Tailscale on every Station on the Fleet." Install on STN2, CUBE, GOG1, TRP0, DPSL, DPSR, STN1, ACHE. ODT already peered as 001-win10pro (100.111.17.67). Per-station: install → tailscale up → record IP in fleet.js. The mesh IS the always-online path — solves DPSL/DPSR/off-fleet reachability structurally.' },
