    { name: 'Orchestra Fleet Map · Pass 3 (color)', filed: '041726', note: 'Follows Pass 2. Color via theme tokens: --ip teal for current Fleet IPs, --obs amber for off-fleet / roaming, --rox red for unresolved phantoms, --head orange for zone titles. Break monospace string into spans with classes. Keep plain-text view copy-pasteable.' },
