    { name: 'Windows 10 fleet policy documented', filed: '041726', note: 'Dan: "Windows side has all Win10 systems and not planning on Win11 until forced." Standing policy. File as STANDARD_RULE_Win10Until_Forced. All NEST.01 Windows tooling targets Win10 compat. No Win11-only features assumed.' },
