    { name: 'GOG1 install-path over SLO-PUB MITM', filed: '041726 23:59', note: 'GOG1 default route (metric 601) goes through SLO-PUB public WiFi with TLS-inspecting proxy injecting self-signed cert. Breaks HTTPS installers (Tailscale curl script failed tonight). Options: (a) apt repo w/ pre-shared PGP, (b) route-metric adjust to copper/VZW temporarily, (c) trust-store install of MITM CA (privacy trade-off), (d) download .deb on ODT w/ clean VZW → scp → dpkg. Option (d) cleanest for one-offs; (b) cleanest for multi-install sessions. Blocks Tailscale-on-GOG1.' },
