    { name: 'UAC rule universalized fleet-wide', filed: '040826', done: '041626', note: 'Removed STN2 scoping. RELAY/STANDARD_RULE_NoUAC_AdminViaRunAs_Trip_040826.md rewritten as universal NEST.01 Windows policy. Per-station verification log: STN2 EnableLUA=0 verified 040826; ODT Never-Notify triplet (EnableLUA=1, ConsentPromptBehaviorAdmin=0, PromptOnSecureDesktop=0) verified 041626 22:00; CUBE verify at commissioning. Memory #12 replaced, #26 retained as ODT registry evidence. Dan: "FUCK UAC TO HELL FOREVER."' },
